name: March 8
description: 4:00. The train arrives to Lviv. The platform is swarming with heads, bags, animals, and babies in arms. Queues for buses to Poland stretched out and took up half the space. Curfew. City transport has to wait two more hours. Arriving people form closely packed groups and huddle around warming fires, waiting for the new open paths. Happy 8th of March, Ukraine.
